questions.question:
Consider the following code:

double foo(int n) {
    int i;
    double sum;
    if (n == 0) {
        return 1.0;
    } else {
        sum = 0.0;
        for (i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            sum += foo(i);
        }
        return sum;
    }
}

The space complexity of the above code is:

A. O(1)
B. O(n)
C. O(n^2)
D. n^n
